name: Lance Of Faith
flavor_text: A brilliant ray of light sears your foe with golden radiance. Sparkles of light linger around the target, guiding your ally’s attack.
hit: 1d8 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage, and one ally you can see gains a +2 power bonus to his or her next at- tack roll against the target.  Increase damage to 2d8 + Wisdom modifier at 21st level.

name: Priest's Shield
flavor_text: You utter a minor defensive prayer as you attack with your weapon.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you and one adjacent ally gain a +1 power bonus to AC until the end of your next turn. Increase damage to 2[W] + Strength modifier at 21st level.

name: Righteous Brand
flavor_text: You smite your foe with your weapon and brand it with a ghostly, glowing symbol of your deity’s anger. By naming one of your allies when the symbol appears, you add divine power to that ally’s attacks against the branded foe.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and one ally within5 squares of you gains a power bonus to melee attack rollsagainst the target equal to your Strength modifier until theend of your next turn. Increase damage to 2[W] + Strength modifier at 21st level.

name: Sacred Flame
flavor_text: Sacred light shines from above, searing a single enemy with its radiance while at the same time aiding an ally with its beneficent power.
hit: 1d6 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage, and one ally you can see chooses either to gain temporary hit pointsequal to your Charisma modifier + one-half your level orto make a saving throw. Increase damage to 2d6 + Wisdom modifier at 21st level.

name: Cause Fear
flavor_text: Your holy symbol ignites with the fury of your god. Uncontrol-lable terror grips your enemy, causing him to instantly recoil.
hit: The target moves its speed + your Charisma modifier away from you. The fleeing target avoids unsafe squaresand difficult terrain if it can. This movement provokes opportunity attacks.

name: Divine Glow
flavor_text: Murmuring a prayer to your deity, you invoke a blast of white radiance from your holy symbol. Foes burn in its stern light, but your allies are heartened and guided by it.
effect: Allies in the blast gain a +2 power bonus to attack rollsuntil the end of your next turn.
hit: 1d8 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage.

name: Healing Strike
flavor_text: Divine radiance gleams from your weapon. When you smite your enemy, your deity bestows a minor blessing in the form of healing for you or one of your allies.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier radiant damage, and the target is marked until the end of your next turn. Inaddition, you or one ally within 5 squares of you can spend a healing surge.

name: Wrathful Thunder
flavor_text: Your arm is made strong by the power of your deity. When you strike, a terrible thunderclap smites your adversary and dazes him.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier thunder damage, and thetarget is dazed until the end of your next turn.

name: Avenging Flame
flavor_text: You slam your weapon into your foe, who bursts into flame. Di-vine fire avenges each attack your enemy dares to make.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and ongoing 5 firedamage (save ends).
miss: Half damage, and no ongoing fire damage.
special: If the target attacks on its turn, it can’t attempt asaving throw against the ongoing damage.

name: Beacon of Hope
flavor_text: A burst of divine energy harms your foes and heals your allies. The radiant energy lingers around your holy symbol and im- proves your healing powers for the rest of the battle.
effect: You and all your allies in the burst regain 5 hit points, and your healing powers restore +5 hit points until the end of the encounter.
hit: The target is weakened until the end of its next turn.

name: Cascade of Light
flavor_text: A burst of divine radiance sears your foe.
hit: 3d8 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage, and the targetgains vulnerability 5 to all your attacks (save ends).
miss: Half damage, and the target gains no vulnerability.

name: Guardian of Faith
flavor_text: You conjure a ghostly guardian, indistinct except for a glowing shield emblazoned with your deity’s symbol. A burst of radiance erupts from it to sear foes that move next to it.
effect: You conjure a guardian that occupies 1 square withinrange. Every round, you can move the guardian 3 squares as a move action. The guardian lasts until the end of the encounter. Any creature that ends its turn next to the con- jured guardian is subject to a Wisdom vs. Fortitude attack. On a hit, the attack deals 1d8 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage.

name: Bless
flavor_text: You beseech your deity to bless you and your allies.
target: You and each ally in burst
effect: Until the end of the encounter, all targets gain a+1 power bonus to attack rolls.

name: Cure Light Wounds
flavor_text: You utter a simple prayer and gain the power to instantly heal wounds, and your touch momentarily suffuses you or a wounded creature with a dim silver light.
effect: The target regains hit points as if it had spent a heal-ing surge.

name: Divine Aid
flavor_text: You beseech your deity to grant you or one of your allies thestrength to overcome a hindrance.
effect: The target makes a saving throw with a bonus equalto your Charisma modifier.

name: Sanctuary
flavor_text: You cast a protective ward upon a creature that makes enemies’attacks less effective.
effect: The target receives a +5 bonus to all defenses. The effect lasts until the target attacks or until the end of your next turn.

name: Shield of Faith
flavor_text: A gleaming shield of divine energy appears over you, grantingyou and nearby allies protection against attacks.
target: You and each ally in burst
effect: The targets gain a +2 power bonus to AC until theend of the encounter.

name: Blazing Beacon
flavor_text: You invoke your deity’s name, and holy light envelops your weapon. When you strike your foe, a blazing beacon in the form of a holy rune floats above its head to guide your allies’ ranged attacks as well.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier radiant damage, and allranged attack rolls against the target gain a +4 power bo- nus until the end of your next turn.

name: Command
flavor_text: You utter a single word to your foe, a word that demands obedi- ence. You can choose to drive the foe back, order it closer, or cause the foe to throw itself to the ground.
hit: The target is dazed until the end of your next turn. In addition, you can choose to knock the target prone orslide the target a number of squares equal to 3 + your Charisma modifier.

name: Daunting Light
flavor_text: A burning column of light engulfs your foe. Its brilliance burnsand hinders your foe’s defense for a short time.
effect: One ally you can see gains combat advantage againstthe target until the end of your next turn.
hit: 2d10 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage.

name: Split the Sky
flavor_text: You invoke ancient words of wrath as you attack with your weap- on. The thundering power of your melee strike causes your foe to stumble backward and fall.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier thunder damage, and youpush the target 2 squares and knock it prone.

name: Consecrated Ground
flavor_text: With a wave of your hand, jagged lines of radiant light spread across the ground around you like a crackling web, moving at your whim. Enemies that stand upon this ground suffer the wrath of your deity.
effect: The burst creates a zone of sanctified ground thatlasts until the end of your next turn. You can move the ori- gin square of the zone 3 squares as a move action. Enemies that start their turns within the zone take 1d6 + your Cha- risma modifier radiant damage. You and any allies who are bloodied and start their turns within the zone regain hit points equal to 1 + your Charisma modifier.

name: Rune of Peace
flavor_text: You smash your weapon into your foe, leaving behind a glowingrune that prevents your foe from making attacks.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and the target can-not attack (save ends).
miss: The target cannot attack you until the end of your nextturn.

name: Spiritual Weapon
flavor_text: You conjure a glowing weapon adorned with the symbol of your deity. The weapon attacks one of your foes and guides your allies’ attacks against the same target.
effect: You conjure a weapon that appears in the target’ssquare and attacks. Your allies gain combat advantage against the target. You can move the weapon up to 10 squares to another enemy’s square as a move action. The weapon lasts until the end of your next turn.
sustain_minor: When you sustain the power, repeat the attack. Your allies continue to gain combat advantage against the weapon’s target.
hit: 1d10 + Wisdom modifier damage.

name: Weapon of the Gods
flavor_text: Your weapon glows with divine radiance, enhancing your attacks.
effect: Until the end of the encounter, all attacks made withthe weapon deal an extra 1d6 radiant damage. When theweapon hits an enemy, the enemy takes a –2 penalty to AC until the end of the weapon wielder’s next turn.

name: Bastion of Health
flavor_text: You invoke a prayer that instantly fortifies one of your allies.
effect: The target can spend a healing surge. Add your Cha-risma modifier to the hit points regained.

name: Cure Serious Wounds
flavor_text: You utter a simple prayer and gain the power to instantly heal wounds, and your touch momentarily suffuses you or a wounded creature with bright silver light.
effect: The target regains hit points as if it had spent twohealing surges.

name: Divine Vigor
flavor_text: You call upon your deity to invigorate you and your battle-wearyallies.
target: You and each target in burst
effect: Each target regains the use of his or her second wind.

name: Holy Lantern
flavor_text: A conjured beacon of divine light shines like a lantern, piercingshadows and deception.
effect: You conjure a lantern that appears in 1 square withinrange and sheds light 5 squares in all directions. You and allies in the light gain a +2 power bonus to Perception andInsight checks. You can move the lantern up to your speed as a minor action. The lantern lasts for 10 hours, but you can have only a single holy lantern active at a time.

name: Awe Strike
flavor_text: The supernatural awe and dread that radiates from you as youswing your weapon leaves your foe momentarily frozen in terror.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and the target is im-mobilized until the end of your next turn.

name: Break the Spirit
flavor_text: Calling down the power of your god, you bathe your foe in ago-nizing radiance, driving strength out of its impending attacks.
hit: 2d8 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage, and the tar- get takes a penalty to attack rolls equal to your Charisma modifier until the end of your next turn.

name: Searing Light
flavor_text: You invoke the power of your deity. From your holy symbol a sear- ing ray of light flashes forth, striking and blinding your enemy for a short time.
hit: 2d6 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage, and the targetis blinded until the end of your next turn.

name: Strengthen the Faithful
flavor_text: You utter a solemn prayer as you bring your weapon down upon your foe, invoking the power of your deity to physically bolster you and nearby allies.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you and eachally adjacent to the target can spend a healing surge. Add your Charisma modifier to the hit points regained.

name: Astral Defenders
flavor_text: You conjure two ghostly soldiers, indistinct except for glowing weapons. They lash out with divine radiance against enemies that pass.
effect: You conjure two soldiers, each occupying 1 squarewithin range. The conjured soldiers don’t attack normally, but whenever an opportunity attack would be provoked from a conjured soldier, the soldier makes a Wisdom vs. Reflex attack. On a hit, the attack deals 1d10 + Wisdom modifier radiant damage.You can move one soldier or both a total of 3 squares as a move action. Creatures can move through the spacesoccupied by the soldiers. The soldiers last until the end of the encounter.

name: Blade Barrier
flavor_text: A barrier of whirling blades appears, slashing at those who cometoo close or try to pass through.
effect: You conjure a wall of contiguous squares filled withspinning blades of astral energy that lasts until the end of your next turn. The wall can be up to 5 squares long and up to 2 squares high. The spaces occupied by the blade barrier are difficult terrain.If a creature enters the barrier’s space or starts its turn there, it takes 3d6 + Wisdom modifier damage plus ongoing 5 damage (save ends).

name: Divine Power
flavor_text: You swing your weapon in a wide arc around you, creating a halo of divine energy that drives foes back while fortifying you and your allies.
target: Each enemy in burst you can see
effect: Until the end of the encounter, you gain regeneration5, and you and each ally within the burst gain a +2 power bonus to AC.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier radiant damage, and you pushthe target 1 square.

name: Clarion Call of the Astral Sea
Cleave
flavor_text: You hit one enemy, then cleave into another.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and an enemy adja-cent to you takes damage equal to your Strength modifier. Increase damage to 2[W] + Strength modifier at 21st level.

name: Reaping Strike
flavor_text: You punctuate your scything attacks with wicked jabs and smallcutting blows that slip through your enemy’s defenses.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage. Increase damage to 2[W] + Strength modifier at 21st level.
miss: Half Strength modifier damage. If you’re wieldinga two-handed weapon, you deal damage equal to your Strength modifier.

name: Sure Strike
flavor_text: You trade power for precision.
hit: Increase damage to 2[W] at 21st level.

name: Tide of Iron
flavor_text: After each mighty swing, you bring your shield to bear and use itto push your enemy back.
requirement: You must be using a shield.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you push thetarget 1 square if it is your size, smaller than you, or onesize category larger. You can shift into the space that thetarget occupied. Increase damage to 2[W] + Strength modifier at 21st level.

name: Covering Attack
flavor_text: You launch a dizzying barrage of thrusts at your enemy, compelling him to give you all his attention. Under the cover of your ferocious attack, one of your allies can safely retreat from that same foe.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and an ally adjacentto the target can shift 2 squares.

name: Passing Attack
flavor_text: You strike at one foe and allow momentum to carry you forwardinto a second strike against a second foe.
secondary_target: One creature other than the primary target
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you can shift1 square. Make a secondary attack.

name: Spinning Sweep
flavor_text: You spin beneath your enemy’s guard with a long, powerful cut, and then sweep your leg through his an instant later to knock him head over heels.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you knock thetarget prone.

name: Steel Serpent Strike
flavor_text: You stab viciously at your foe’s knee or foot to slow him down. Nomatter how tough he is, he’s going to favor that leg for a time.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and the target isslowed and cannot shift until end of your next turn.

name: Brute Strike
flavor_text: You shatter armor and bone with a ringing blow.
hit: 3[W] + Strength modifier damage.

name: Comeback Strike
flavor_text: A timely strike against a hated foe invigorates you, giving you thestrength and resolve to fight on.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you can spend ahealing surge.

name: Villan's Menace
flavor_text: You strike your enemy hard and hound him with skilled parriesand stern reprisals.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and you gain a+2 power bonus to attack rolls and a +4 power bonusto damage rolls against the target until the end of theencounter.
miss: Gain a +1 power bonus to attack rolls and a +2 powerbonus to damage rolls against the target until the end of the encounter.

name: Boundless Endurance
flavor_text: You shake off the worst of your wounds.
effect: You gain regeneration 2 + your Constitution modifier when you are bloodied.

name: Get Over Here
flavor_text: You pull one of your allies into a more advantageous position.
effect: You slide the target 2 squares to a square that is ad-jacent to you.

name: No Opening
flavor_text: You raise your weapon or shield to block an opening in yourdefenses.
trigger: An enemy attacks you and has combat advantage against you
effect: Cancel the combat advantage you were about to grant to the attack.

name: Unstoppable
flavor_text: You let your adrenaline surge carry you through the battle.
effect: You gain temporary hit points equal to 2d6 + yourConstitution modifier.

name: Armor Piercing Thrust
flavor_text: You drive your weapon through a weak point in your foe’sdefenses.
hit: If you’re wielding a light blade or a spear, you gain a bonus to the damage roll equal to your Dexterity modifier.
weapon_attack_mod: If you’re wielding a light blade or a spear, you gaina bonus to the attack roll equal to your Dexterity modifier.

name: Crushing Blow
flavor_text: You wind up and deliver a devastating blow with your weapon.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage.
weapon_hit_mod: If you’re wielding an axe, a hammer, or a mace, you gain a bonus to the damage roll equal to your Constitution modifier.

name: Dance of Steel
flavor_text: Weaving your weapon in a graceful figure-eight, you lash outwith a sudden attack.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage.
weapon_hit_mod: If you’re wielding a polearm or a heavy blade, the target is slowed until the end of your next turn.

name: Precise Strike
flavor_text: You trade damage for accuracy when you really want to land anattack on your opponent.
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage.

name: Rain of Blows
flavor_text: You become a blur of motion, raining a series of blows upon youropponent.
secondary_target: The same or a different target
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage.
weapon_hit_mod: If you’re wielding a light blade, a spear, or a flail and have Dexterity 15 or higher, make a secondary attack.

name: Sweeping Blow
flavor_text: You put all your strength into a single mighty swing that strikesmany enemies at once.
target: Each enemy in burst you can see
hit: 1[W] + Strength modifier damage.
weapon_hit_mod: If you’re wielding an axe, a flail, a heavy blade, or a pick, you gain a bonus to the attack roll equal to one-half your Strength modifier.

name: Crack the Shell
flavor_text: You break through your enemy’s armor and deal a painful bleed-ing wound.
hit: 2[W] + Strength modifier damage, and the target takes ongoing 5 damage and a –2 penalty to AC (save ends both).

name: Dizzying Blow
flavor_text: You crack your foe upside the head.
hit: 3[W] + Strength modifier damage, and the target isimmobilized (save ends).

name: Rain of Steel
flavor_text: You constantly swing your weapon about, slashing and cuttinginto nearby enemies.
effect: Any enemy that starts its turn adjacent to you takes1[W] damage, as long as you are able to make opportunity attacks.

name: To the Nine Hells with You
